Package org.hibernate.engine.spi

Interface SessionFactoryImplementor

All Superinterfaces:
AutoCloseable, BindingContext, EntityManagerFactory, MappingContext, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver, Referenceable, Serializable, SessionFactory, SqlAstCreationContext, SqmCreationContext
All Known Implementing Classes:
MockSessionFactory, ProcessorSessionFactory, SessionFactoryDelegatingImpl, SessionFactoryImpl
public interface SessionFactoryImplementor extends MappingContext, SessionFactory, SqmCreationContext, SqlAstCreationContext, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver
Defines the internal contract between the SessionFactory and the internal implementation of Hibernate.
